  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This assessment evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. The intended use is regulatory submission support for a Class III implantable VAD operating at 6000–9000 RPM in patients with end-stage heart failure. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed. All 13 credibility factors have been assessed and the composite credibility score meets the threshold for the declared model risk level. Decision: Accepted.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-cfd-hemolysis-absolute-prediction",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/cfd-hemolysis-centrifugal-pump-v3",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-generic-pump-piv-dataset",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/hemolysis-in-vitro-validation-set"
  ],
